== Open File with Root Rights ==
Prefer <code>sudoedit</code> for better security. <ref>
https://forums.whonix.org/t/use-sudoedit-in-whonix-documentation/7599
</ref> Replace <code>/path/to/file</code> with the actual file name.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudoedit /path/to/file
}}

To use a different editor. Replace <code>mousepad</code> with the name of the editor you wish to use.

{{CodeSelect|code=
SUDO_EDITOR=mousepad sudoedit /path/to/file
}}

{{Box|text=
An alternative would be to install these tools <code>lxsudo</code> and <code>mousepad</code> so you can keep copying and pasting these instructions.
{{Box|text=
{{Install Package|package=
--no-install-recommends sudo lxsudo mousepad
}}
}}

{{CodeSelect|code=
lxsudo mousepad /path/to/file
}}
}}

